<span class="newsitem">Another editorial on video game violence. Has our industry seen enough of these? Oh, you bet. Are we getting tired of reading them? Absolutely. So is another one rehashing the subject warranted? Hellchick thinks it's warranted until someone makes John Ashcroft realize he's completely misplacing the blame in his recent statements on video game violence.
