this point, so I have not been very diligent in my rune getting I'm
sorry to say. However, I still have the bag left over from the last
trade, and I am in want of none myself, so I will be there to hand out
alcohol, give out what runes I have, and just have fun with my fellow
wizards. All are invited to attend, be they wizards or not.
